          <h2 id="examples">Examples</h2>

<h3 id="default">Default</h3>

<div class="site-showcase" style="max-width: 100%">
  <iframe width="100%" height="" src="/storybook/iframe.html?id=uswds-va-accordion--default&amp;viewMode=story"></iframe>
</div>

<p><a href="/storybook/?path=/docs/uswds-va-accordion--default"><img aria-hidden="true" role="img" src="/images/storybook.svg" class="site-component-resources-links__icon" width="16px" alt="Storybook logo" />View va-accordion default in Storybook</a></p>

<h3 id="bordered">Bordered</h3>

<div class="site-showcase" style="max-width: 100%">
  <iframe width="100%" height="" src="/storybook/iframe.html?id=uswds-va-accordion--bordered&amp;viewMode=story"></iframe>
</div>

<p><a href="/storybook/?path=/docs/uswds-va-accordion--bordered"><img aria-hidden="true" role="img" src="/images/storybook.svg" class="site-component-resources-links__icon" width="16px" alt="Storybook logo" />View va-accordion bordered in Storybook</a></p>

<h3 id="single-select">Single Select</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Adding an <code>open-single</code> prop on the <code>va-accordion</code> component will allow the user to only open one accordion at a time.</li>
</ul>

<div class="site-showcase" style="max-width: 100%">
  <iframe width="100%" height="" src="/storybook/iframe.html?id=uswds-va-accordion--single-select&amp;viewMode=story"></iframe>
</div>

<p><a href="/storybook/?path=/docs/uswds-va-accordion--single-select"><img aria-hidden="true" role="img" src="/images/storybook.svg" class="site-component-resources-links__icon" width="16px" alt="Storybook logo" />View va-accordion single select in Storybook</a></p>

<h3 id="subheader">Subheader</h3>

<div class="site-showcase" style="max-width: 100%">
  <iframe width="100%" height="" src="/storybook/iframe.html?id=uswds-va-accordion--subheader&amp;viewMode=story"></iframe>
</div>

